<p>Go to <strong>Setup Â» CMS Â» Forms</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings as desired. Pay attention to the information given in <a href="#table-create-new-form">Table 1</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.<br>
â†’ The new form is not listed in the overview of <strong>FORMS</strong> until you have reloaded the menu.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
