<div class="sect3">
<h4 id="_changing_a_form">4.2.3. Changing a form</h4>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Proceed as follows in order to change the settings of a previously saved form.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Changing a form:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Setup Â» CMS Â» Forms</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the form that you want to change from the overview of <strong>FORMS</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Pay attention to the explanations given in <a href="#table-create-new-form">Table 1</a> and make the changes as desired.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="admonitionblock important">
