<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">The following information provides a quick overview of the management functions. These functions are explained in more detail on the <a href="/en/omni-channel/online-store/setting-up-clients/cms#web-design-editing-the-web-design">Editing the web design</a> page of the manual.<br>
