</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>//  txt</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Comments that are inserted to help users find their way around in the code. These comments will not be displayed. They are used, e.g. to segment iterations in lists.</p></td>
