<div class="title">Do not delete important content from the template!</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The <strong>$MainFrame</strong> template variable is a necessary element of a template and may not be removed. Otherwise the dynamic main content will not be displayed. Comments should not be deleted from the template either.</p>
</div>
