<div class="sect5">
<h6 id="_template_variable_mainframe">Template variable MainFrame</h6>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The template variable <strong>$MainFrame</strong> displays the dynamic content, e.g. the detailed view of an item with the template <strong>ItemViewSingleItem</strong> or the <strong>category view</strong> with the template <strong>ItemViewCategoriesList</strong>. The template variable is used in every PageDesign.</p>
</div>
