<div class="sect4">
<h5 id="_cms_editors_2">CMS editors</h5>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>A new editor is available starting with plentymarkets version 5.1. Apart from the familiar <strong>editor</strong> (CKEditor) and the conventional <strong>text field</strong>, plentymarkets also provides the new <strong>syntax editor</strong> to edit html content such as item descriptions, templates, categories of the type <strong>content</strong> and email templates. Broadly speaking, the syntax editor is a professional alternative to the <strong>text field</strong> because it not only includes syntax highlighting but also further functions that increase your level of comfort and efficiency when editing HTML.</p>
</div>
