<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Content</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter the quantity that the price calculation should be based upon. In the example, this is per 100 square centimeters.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Length</strong></p></td>
