<div class="sect3 adoc">
<h4 id="web-design-editing-the-web-design-misc">5.5.9. Misc</h4>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>CMS Â» Web design Â» Layout Â» Misc</strong></p>
</div>
<div class="sect4">
<h5 id="_general_information_2">General information</h5>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>These templates control how deadlines, FAQs and customer registration are designed in your online store. Configuration is carried out in two steps. First decide which information the template variables should return and carry out the corresponding settings. Then decide where this information should be displayed in the online store and insert the template variable at this location in the category page or layout template. The following sections show you how to configure deadlines, FAQs and the customer registration.</p>
</div>
<div class="admonitionblock important">
<table>
<tbody><tr>
<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-important" title="Important"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
