<p>The plentymarkets CMS validators make sure that your customers entered valid information during the order process. The server validates all of the data that customers entered before saving this data in the database. For example, it makes sure that email addresses have the correct format. It also makes sure that entry fields such as the street and house number use meaningful combinations of letters and numbers. The validators are found in your plentymarkets system under <strong>CMS Â» Web design Â» Layout Â» Validator</strong>. The following validators are relevant to the order process:</p>
