<div class="paragraph">
<p>In this submenu, you can determine which fields should be <strong>mandatory</strong> for customers to fill out.</p>
</div>
<div class="admonitionblock warning">
<table>
<tbody><tr>
<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-warning" title="Warning"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="title">Telephone number as a mandatory field</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>It is useful to have a telephone number where you can contact customers in case of questions. If a telephone number is not listed, then you will receive an error message for shipments to other countries when transferring data to DHL Intraship. This is because DHL has made the telephone number a mandatory field for foreign shipments.</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</div>
</div>
