<div class="title">Unused</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The <strong>Unused</strong> folder contains CSS areas that were not configured or that were left blank for a different reason. If the CSS is completely deleted from a menu item, then it will be moved into this folder.</p>
</div>
</td>
