<p>If you want to generate a link to a specific blog entry, e.g. within another blog entry or in a template that does not include the word "blog" in its name, then insert the <strong>Link_Blog()</strong> function with the corresponding ID. The example preview list in <a href="#image-preview-list-one-blog-entry">Figure 65</a> only consists of blog entry 16 because the ID 16 was added to the function.</p>
