</div>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="_attaching_documents_to_email_templates">11.3. Attaching documents to email templates</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can automatically attach the documents that were uploaded to email templates. To do so, proceed as follows.</p>
</div>
