<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="_editing_deadlines">12.2. Editing deadlines</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Creating a new deadline:</strong></p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Deadlines</strong> (see path above).</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the green <strong>plus icon</strong> to create a new deadline.<br>
â†’ An editing window will open.</p>
</li>
