<p>Enter information about the deadline.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.<br>
â†’ The deadline will be displayed in the <strong>preview</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Editing a deadline:</strong></p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Deadlines</strong> and open the <strong>preview</strong> tab (see path above).</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the <strong>pencil icon</strong> to edit a deadline.<br>
â†’ The deadlineâ€™s editing window will open.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Make <strong>changes/additions</strong> as desired.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Searching for a deadline:</strong></p>
</div>
