</li>
<li>
<p>Select the <strong>time period</strong> by entering a starting date in the field <strong>from</strong> and an ending date in the field <strong>to</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the <strong>magnifying glass</strong>.<br>
â†’ The deadline(s) for this time period will be displayed.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
