<div class="sect3">
<h4 id="_uploading_the_new_version">16.1.2. Uploading the new version</h4>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Proceed as described below to upload the new version of plentymarketsCMStools-x.x.x.js and plentymarketsCMStools-x.x.x.min.js into the webspace of your plentymarkets system.</p>
</div>
