<li>
<p>Go to <strong>CMS Â» Webspace</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Open the folder <strong>layout Â» Your design Â» js Â» plenty</strong>.<br>
â†’ Expand the folders by clicking on the small plus sign on the left.</p>
